ROCK
v.
EXECUTIVE OFFICE PARK OF DURHAM ASSOCIATION, INC. 428P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 21, 2017 Martin E. Rock, for Rock, Martin E. J. Matthew Waters, Attorney at Law, Hope Derby Carmichael, Attorney at Law, Raleigh, for Executive Office Park of Durham Association, Inc.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of December 2017 by Respondent to Reconsider:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 21st of December 2017."
